												<p>Golden Bridge Enterprises (Aust) Pty Ltd respects the privacy of our customers, and accordingly has implemented this Privacy and Security Policy Statement to explain our online privacy and security policies.&nbsp; </p>
												<p><strong>Information Collection</strong> <br>
