  1.Non-public, personal information you knowingly choose to disclose, which is collected on an individual basis via internet, fax, phone, or mail. <br>
  2.Website use information collected on an aggregate basis as you and others browse our website. If you choose to correspond through e-mail, we may retain the content of your e-mail messages together with your e-mail address and all responses sent through our website. We provide the same protections for these electronic communications as we employ in the maintenance of information received by mail and telephone. <br>
  3.Information we receive from you on applications or other forms. <br>
  4.Information about your transactions with affiliated and non-affiliated third parties. <br>
  5.Information we obtain to verify representations made by you, such as your checking account information. <br>
  6.Information we obtain from a person regarding their employment, or other relationship with you, such as your employment history. </p>
												<p><strong>Information Disclosure</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>
  Golden Bridge Enterprises (Aust) Pty Ltd may disclose non-public, personal information to non-affiliated third parties such as collection agencies, as permitted by law. Nonpublic personal information means information about you that we collect in connection with providing a financial product or service to you. Nonpublic personal information does not include information that is available from public sources, such as telephone directories or government records. </p>
												<p>Golden Bridge Enterprises (Aust) Pty Ltd may use information collected via correspondence to send you marketing communications which could include payment notices, account updates, information about website changes, new Golden Bridge Enterprises (Aust) Pty Ltd products and services, and special offers. The lists used to send you product and service offers are developed and managed to safeguard personal information. </p>
												<p><strong>Information Transfer Security</strong> <br>
  Golden Bridge Enterprises (Aust) Pty Ltd uses the latest security measures to ensure your private personal cash loan information remains private. <br>
  <br>
  All information you submit to us is encrypted to protect your privacy. We maintain physical, electronic, and procedural safeguards to protect any information we have about you. You can rest assured your loan application will always remain private at Golden Bridge Enterprises (Aust) Pty Ltd. </p>
												<p><strong>Children's Online Privacy Protection Act</strong> <br>
